FitStreak - Project Report
Executive Summary
Project Name: FitStreak
Project Type: Web Application (Fitness Tracking Platform)
Development Framework: Laravel 12 (PHP) with Vite & Tailwind CSS
Status: In Development
Repository: SmashCode001100/fitstreak

FitStreak is a comprehensive fitness tracking and motivation platform designed to help users build consistent workout habits through streak tracking, achievement systems, and gamification elements. The application enables users to log workouts, track progress over time, earn achievements, and maintain motivation through visual progress indicators and milestone celebrations.

1. Project Overview
1.1 Purpose & Objectives
FitStreak addresses the fitness domain by providing:

Habit Tracking: Users can maintain workout streaks and monitor consistency
Progress Monitoring: Comprehensive metrics and progress visualization
Gamification: Achievement system with XP and leveling mechanics
User Engagement: Reminders, notifications, and goal-setting features
Personalization: User customization through onboarding and settings
1.2 Target Users
Individual fitness enthusiasts seeking streak-based motivation
Users looking for workout habit tracking
Athletes and casual gym-goers wanting progress visualization
Users motivated by achievement systems and gamification
1.3 Key Features
Core Features
User Authentication & Onboarding: Multi-step onboarding process for personalized setup
Workout Logging: Track completed workouts with multiple exercises
Streak Tracking: Monitor workout consistency and maintain streaks
Progress Dashboard: Real-time overview of fitness metrics and progress
Calendar View: Visual representation of workout history
Achievement System: Unlock achievements based on milestones
XP & Leveling: Gamified progression system
User Reminders: Workout reminders and notifications
Secondary Features
Profile Management: User profile customization
Settings Panel: Application preferences and timezone configuration
Metrics Tracking: Advanced fitness metrics (custom metrics support)
Notification System: Real-time user notifications
2. Technical Architecture
2.1 Technology Stack
Layer	Technologies
Backend Framework	Laravel 12.0
Language	PHP 8.2+
Frontend	Vue.js/Blade Templates, Alpine.js
Styling	Tailwind CSS 3.1, PostCSS
Build Tool	Vite 7.0.7
Database	SQLite (Development), PostgreSQL/MySQL (Production-ready)
API Communication	Axios 1.11
Package Manager	Composer (PHP), npm (JavaScript)
Testing	PHPUnit 11.5.50
Development Tools	Laravel Sail, Laravel Pint (Linter), Laravel Breeze
