XP and level progression
Progress Tracking
View historical metrics
Calendar visualization of workouts
Performance trends
Achievement progress
Streak Management
Current streak counter
Longest streak record
Streak reset on missed days
Motivation through consistency tracking
Achievements
Browse available achievements
View earned achievements with timestamps
Track achievement progress
Unlock achievements through milestones
