6. Application Routes & Navigation
6.1 Public Routes
Route	Purpose
/	Welcome/landing page
6.2 Authenticated Routes
Onboarding
GET /onboarding/step-1 - Onboarding step 1
GET /onboarding/step-2 - Onboarding step 2
GET /onboarding/step-3 - Onboarding step 3
POST /onboarding - Store onboarding data
Core Application (Post-Onboarding)
Route	Purpose
GET /dashboard	Main dashboard
GET /workouts	Workout list
GET /workouts/{id}	Workout details
POST /workouts/{id}/complete	Complete workout
GET /calendar	Calendar view
GET /progress	Progress metrics
GET /streaks	Streak overview
GET /achievements	Achievements
GET /settings	Settings page
GET /profile	Edit profile
PATCH /profile	Update profile
DELETE /profile	Delete profile
7. Code Quality & Standards
7.1 Code Organization
PSR-4 Autoloading: Organized namespace structure
