7.3 Security Considerations
Authentication: Laravel Breeze for secure user auth
Authorization: Middleware for route protection
Database: Password hashing, parameterized queries
Email Security: Resend integration for email delivery
8. Performance & Scalability
8.1 Optimization Strategies
Database: Efficient Eloquent queries with eager loading
