Queue System: Background job processing for heavy operations
8.2 Scalability
Stateless Design: Authentication via session/tokens
Database Agnostic: Support for multiple database backends
Cloud Ready: Vercel deployment configuration
Load Balancing: Compatible with standard web server load balancing
