11. Conclusion
FitStreak is a well-architected fitness tracking platform built with modern web technologies. The application successfully implements core features for workout tracking, streak maintenance, and gamified progress monitoring. The codebase demonstrates good separation of concerns, follows Laravel conventions, and is positioned for scalability and feature expansion.

The project is suitable for deployment to production and provides a solid foundation for continued development and enhancement of fitness tracking capabilities.

